data.title: Enlightened rocks
data.text:
Hi! Good to see you!

This website is intended for the registration and verification of all Enlightened agents.

If you don't know what that means, you probably aren't playing Ingress.

Please login to confirm your identity. If you have multiple accounts for Google, please use the one you are most active with in Google+ communities.

About Ingress

Ingress is a location-based game for smartphones, created by Niantic Inc.

Niantic Inc. and also the communities are arranging competitive and cooperative events over the world.

About enlightened.rocks

enlightened.rocks assists the ENL communities in keeping the organization overhead small and setting up a profile and network for all agents. It was created to keep a central backend for faster anomaly verification and to get rid of endless Google forms with the same questions every time.
